high_descs: Walk around the center table to face the counter on the opposite side of the room.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk around to face the opposite end of the center table.
Cut the apple on the center table into three pieces.
Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around to step forward to face the center table.
Pick up the apple piece on the center table.
Walk around the center table to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Place the piece of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a heated piece of apple in the sink with a knife.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the butter knife next to the pan.
Turn around and go to the far side of the island.
Slice the apple in the center of the island.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the island.
Pick up a slice of apple from the center of the island.
Go past the fridge on the left to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink to the left.
Put the hot apple slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot apple slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the toaster.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the center counter.
Cut an apple on the center counter.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn and go to the center counter.
Put up a slice of apple on the center counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the slice of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of apple in the sink.
